OL,5, An 87-year-old woman who did not heat  
OL,6, her home because she was worried about 
OL,7, high energy bills died after she was   
OL,8, found suffering from profound          
OL,9, hypothermia.                           
OL,11,FBarbara Bolton's inquest was told she  
OL,12,Fhad ignored pleas from her family to   
OL,13,Fheat her terraced house in Bury.       
OL,15,FShe was discovered by her grandson at  
OL,16,Fher kitchen table, unable to speak, on 
OL,17,F11 December and later died in hospital.
OL,19,FA conclusion of misadventure was       
OL,20,Frecorded by the coroner in Rochdale.   
